#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:2
#: 5a0b1f91a66c4f288c3e210237d13b3b
msgid "安装指南"
msgstr "Installation Guide"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:4
#: 498e25b4628b4f18bf8e7c8ee14745e6
msgid "本页说明如何把 Godot-FmodPlayer 安装到 Godot 项目中，并补齐 FMOD Core API 运行库。推荐优先使用预编译版本；只有需要修改插件源码或自行适配平台时，才需要从源码构建。"
msgstr ""
"This page explains how to install Godot-FmodPlayer into a Godot project and add the required FMOD Core API runtime libraries. In most cases, use the prebuilt package. Build from source only when you need to modify the plugin source code or adapt it to another platform."

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:8
#: a1c0503362994171a3c777022c1d8123
msgid "安装前确认"
msgstr "Before You Start"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:10
#: 2a20c87b80b84ddd9d65ea0545f39328
msgid "开始前请确认："
msgstr "Before you begin, make sure that:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:12
#: 920f0168f5824b3a8467af6ec54aa6c6
msgid "Godot 版本为 4.1 或更高版本。"
msgstr "Your Godot version is 4.1 or later."

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:13
#: 15200fc6b4bc4728b1029965dc8a281a
msgid "目标平台目前为 Windows x86_64 或 Android arm64。"
msgstr "Your target platform is currently Windows x86_64 or Android arm64."

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:14
#: f6dd079c56d24605a8d0be317108f356
msgid "已准备好从 FMOD 官网下载 FMOD Engine。"
msgstr "You are ready to download FMOD Engine from the official FMOD website."

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:18
#: 3c9ed0a52d9e410d9df9943b9c97cdb0
msgid ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer 插件本身不包含 FMOD 运行库。由于 FMOD 的许可要求， 你需要自行从 `FMOD 下载页面 <https://www.fmod.com/download>`_ 获取 FMOD Engine，并把对应平台的运行库复制到项目中。"
msgstr ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer does not include the FMOD runtime libraries. Because of FMOD licensing requirements, you must download FMOD Engine yourself from the `FMOD download page <https://www.fmod.com/download>`_ and copy the runtime libraries for your target platform into the project."

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:23
#: 1faa7ec1fcb746539fa1fd88f7196616
msgid "预编译版本（推荐）"
msgstr "Prebuilt Package (Recommended)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:26
#: 51efbc4a6aed40b1944a693ceb902f12
msgid "下载插件"
msgstr "Download the Plugin"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:28
#: 3e1ce6d2c4db4fb18adfbaadc4de92c7
msgid ""
"从 `Godot Asset Library <https://godotengine.org/asset-library/asset/4905>`_ 下载插件，或从 `GitHub Releases <https://github.com/LuYingYiLong/Godot-FmodPlayer/releases>`_ 下载发布包。"
msgstr ""
"Download the plugin from the `Godot Asset Library <https://godotengine.org/asset-library/asset/4905>`_, or download a release package from `GitHub Releases <https://github.com/LuYingYiLong/Godot-FmodPlayer/releases>`_."

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:32
#: 1125cb21683f46819438421b6d9db103
msgid "解压后，将 ``addons/fmod_player`` 复制到你的 Godot 项目："
msgstr "After extracting the package, copy ``addons/fmod_player`` into your Godot project:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:34
#: 34bbf77be03c4efaa7a7a7a3c62a53ed
msgid ""
"res://\n"
"└── addons/\n"
"    └── fmod_player/\n"
"        ├── plugin.cfg\n"
"        ├── fmod_check.gd\n"
"        ├── fmod_player_main.gd\n"
"        └── bin/\n"
"            ├── fmod_player.gdextension\n"
"            ├── fmod_player.windows.template_debug.x86_64.dll\n"
"            ├── fmod_player.windows.template_release.x86_64.dll\n"
"            ├── libfmod_player.android.template_debug.arm64.so\n"
"            └── libfmod_player.android.template_release.arm64.so"
msgstr ""
"res://\n"
"└── addons/\n"
"    └── fmod_player/\n"
"        ├── plugin.cfg\n"
"        ├── fmod_check.gd\n"
"        ├── fmod_player_main.gd\n"
"        └── bin/\n"
"            ├── fmod_player.gdextension\n"
"            ├── fmod_player.windows.template_debug.x86_64.dll\n"
"            ├── fmod_player.windows.template_release.x86_64.dll\n"
"            ├── libfmod_player.android.template_debug.arm64.so\n"
"            └── libfmod_player.android.template_release.arm64.so"

