msgid "打开 Godot 输出面板，确认没有 FMOD 运行库缺失或 GDExtension 加载失败的错误。"
msgstr "Open Godot's Output panel and confirm that there are no missing FMOD runtime errors or GDExtension loading errors."

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:112
#: 0bab1cd4b6d847bd919d8dccfbd21f2d
msgid "如果节点或资源类型没有出现，通常是 FMOD 运行库缺失、平台架构不匹配，或 ``addons/fmod_player`` 没有放在项目的 ``res://addons/`` 目录下。"
msgstr ""
"If the node or resource types do not appear, the usual causes are a missing FMOD runtime library, a platform architecture mismatch, or ``addons/fmod_player`` not being placed under the project's ``res://addons/`` directory."

